\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"https://www.agentimage.com/?p=25338\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:781:\"<p><img class=\"rss-ai-feed\" src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/10-best-real-estate-websites-for-may-2022-300x99.jpg\">As May and spring come to an end, the hectic summer real estate season begins. Its a good thing these agents and teams have brand-new websites that give them an edge in todays competitive property market. From classic to contemporary and everything in between, this months selection of the best real estate websites highlights how [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/blog/10-best-real-estate-websites-for-may-2022/\">10 Best Real Estate Websites For May 2022</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.agentimage.com\">Best Real Estate Websites for Agents and Brokers</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"AgentImage\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23413:\"<img class=\"rss-ai-feed\" src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/10-best-real-estate-websites-for-may-2022-300x99.jpg\"><div class=\"custom-entry\">\n<p>As May and spring come to an end, the hectic summer real estate season begins.</p>\n<p>Its a good thing these agents and teams have brand-new websites that give them an edge in todays competitive property market.</p>\n<p>From classic to contemporary and everything in between, this months selection of the best real estate websites highlights how great design can help you get great business results.</p>\n<h3>Melanie Miller <span>Lake Mary, FL</span></h3>\n<p>Sun-kissed and sophisticated, Melanie Millers website captures the prestige of living in Lake Mary, FL. Rather than a static banner section, her site uses an immersive video that showcases the leafy neighborhoods, verdant fairways, and amazing houses in this neighborhood. Gold is used as an accent color to further highlight the deluxe properties and white-glove service that Melanie provides to her discerning clients.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> The banner video opens with animated typography that resembles a handwritten signature &#8211; a nod to the realtors hands-on approach.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/sellingcentral.jpg\" alt=\"Melanie Miller\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710361539?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"Melanie Miller\" href=\"http://www.sellingcentral.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - Melanie Miller\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>Katie Reid <span>Atlanta, GA</span></h3>\n<p>Katie Reid was once an educator so helping others fulfill their dreams comes naturally to her. She has parlayed this philosophy to real estate, where she now assists buyers and sellers in getting the most rewarding deal possible. Her genuine care and passion translate to her website as well. Gray tones reinforce her credibility and authority, while shades of beige connote her warm personality. Her website has a simple layout for ease of navigation, ensuring that everything you need is just a scroll away.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> Finding your dream home has never been easier thanks to the interactive map, which conveniently clusters listings by neighborhood.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/kreidrealtygroup.jpg\" alt=\"Katie Reid\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710361613?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"Katie Reid\" href=\"http://kreidrealtygroup.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - Katie Reid\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>Lake Anna Home <span>Chesapeake, VA</span></h3>\n<p>The Berger Team stands out because it adds immense value to each clients real estate experience. This is echoed in their unconventional but impressive website that bucks the status quo by using horizontal scrolling. Not only does this design decision pique interest, but it also creates a more immersive experience and provides a wider canvas for LakeAnnaHome.coms many useful features. Whether you need a free appraisal or a comparative market analysis (CMA), this website has you covered.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> Another outstanding feature of LakeAnnaHome.com is its virtual staging section, which features a before and after photo of a room. Just use the scrolling divider to see how the space is transformed from spare to sophisticated.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/lakeannahome.jpg\" alt=\"Lake Anna Home\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710361700?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"Lake Anna Home\" href=\"https://www.lakeannahome.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - Lake Anna Home\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>Zac Mostame <span>Los Angeles, CA</span></h3>\n<p>Los Angeles is a place where you can live large. Fittingly, Zac Mostames website features full-screen photos that embody the appeal of Southern California living. This image-centric approach extends to the featured properties, too, which are laid out in an asymmetric, collage-like arrangement. Meanwhile, the black-and-white theme lends the site a simple but elegant look.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> Immersion leads to conversions. Thats why ZMEstates.com features a video section that offers walkthroughs of some of Zacs most prized listings.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/zacmostame.jpg\" alt=\"Zac Mostame\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710361779?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"Zac Mostame\" href=\"http://www.zacmostame.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - Zac Mostame\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>Jamie McMartin <span>Katy, TX</span></h3>\n<p>TheJamieMcMartinGroup.com oozes sophistication thanks to its classy black-and-white color palette. As you scroll through or hover over items, however, colors come to life. For this project, we went with an uncluttered design thats simple but doesnt scrimp on style. Animated visual elements that snap into place along with the parallax effect give the site a sense of dynamism.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> While the featured listings are presented as a grid, hovering over one of them will transform the adjacent tiles into the selected property, creating a mosaic-like effect.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/thejamiemcmartingroup.jpg\" alt=\"Jamie McMartin\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710361851?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"Jamie McMartin\" href=\"https://www.thejamiemcmartingroup.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - Jamie McMartin\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>Neil Spencer <span>Denver, CO</span></h3>\n<p>NeilSpencerCo.com is bursting with color  and rightly so given the stunning sights of Colorado. The screen-to-screen photos showcase these vistas to full effect, while the quick search function makes it easy to find your dream home in this picturesque place. Below the fold, generous white space serves as a canvas for the equally captivating photos of luxury homes, while blue and gray visual elements create a professional yet modern look.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> Neils stylized initials feature prominently not just above the fold but elsewhere on the site, too. For instance, if you hover over a listing, the logo will be subtly superimposed on the image. A neat way to tie in agent branding!</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/neilspencerco.jpg\" alt=\"Neil Spencer\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710361933?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"Neil Spencer\" href=\"https://neilspencerco.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - Neil Spencer\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>Red Frog Beach <span>Panama</span></h3>\n<p>The moment RedFrogProperty.com loads, you are whisked away to a world of white-sand shores, lush forests, tropical cocktails, and stunning mountainside homes. Indeed, immersion was the order of the day when designing this website thats dedicated to real estate in Bocas del Toro, Panama. Featured properties and communities are rendered almost like postcards  a little taste of this paradise that site visitors could soon call home.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> Eager to purchase property in this seaside community? You can reach out to Red Frog Beachs team by clicking on the WhatsApp chat function on the bottom right.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/redfrogproperty.jpg\" alt=\"Red Frog Beach\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710362015?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"Red Frog Beach\" href=\"https://www.redfrogproperty.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - Red Frog Beach\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>IMS Realty <span>Las Vegas, NV</span></h3>\n<p>As the saying  goes: What happens in Vegas, stays in Vegas. But after visiting IMS Realtys website, youll be pining to be back in the city before long. Thats because LuxBrokerTeam.com gives you a peek not just into the thrumming nightlife of Las Vegas, but also its tranquil suburbs and nearby natural wonders. Thoughtful design touches are found throughout the site, from the images fused into the background to the gold accent colors that add sophistication.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> There is no shortage of excellent neighborhoods around Las Vegas, and the interactive map offers a convenient way to explore which one best suits your lifestyle.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/luxbrokerteam.jpg\" alt=\"IMS Realty\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710362081?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"IMS Realty\" href=\"https://luxbrokerteam.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - IMS Realty\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>HOME Luxury Real Estate <span>Atlanta, GA</span></h3>\n<p>HomeGeorgia.com has a stately and high-gloss look that wouldnt be out of place in an interior design magazine. This is made possible by crisp images, abundant white space, highly readable fonts, and a streamlined layout. Of course, this website is just as much a delight to use as it is to peruse, thanks to portals for buyers, sellers, and those looking for agents.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> The aesthetics arent the only thing impressive about HomeGeorgia.com. A section on its phenomenal sales record demonstrates the skill and talent of this year-old real estate team.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/homegeorgia.jpg\" alt=\"HOME Luxury Real Estate\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710362177?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"HOME Luxury Real Estate\" href=\"https://www.homegeorgia.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - HOME Luxury Real Estate\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h3>Katerina Sayles <span>Issaquah, WA</span></h3>\n<p>Browsing through Katerina Sayles website is almost like scrolling through an Instagram page. Not only are the photos of homes and vistas impressive, but the website also uses a grid-like layout. Transparency and color gradients are also used throughout the site to create a greater sense of depth.</p>\n<p><strong>What&#8217;s unique about this website?</strong> The website is one of the rare ones to have a section for green home searches. This makes it easier to find a comfortable but eco-friendly abode in the Northwest.</p>\n<div class=\"vid-wrap\">\n		<img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/katerinasaylesrealtor.jpg\" alt=\"Katerina Sayles\" class=\"img-responsive\"><br />\n		<iframe src=\"https://player.vimeo.com/video/710362294?background=1&#038;autoplay=1&#038;loop=1&#038;autopause=0&#038;title=0&#038;byline=0&#038;portrait=0\" width=\"823\" height=\"365\" frameborder=\"0\" webkitallowfullscreen mozallowfullscreen allowfullscreen></iframe>\n	</div>\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"Katerina Sayles\" href=\"https://www.katerinasaylesrealtor.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"orange-radius-144 white-radius-144 center-block\">View Website</a>\n		</div>\n<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n			<a product-name=\"GPF - Katerina Sayles\" href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"seo-product-bttn orange-radius-144 center-block desktop-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/get-pricing-and-features/\" class=\"orange-radius-144 center-block mobile-view\">Get Pricing &amp; Features</a>\n		</div>\n</p></div>\n<h2>Recap of standout features</h2>\n<p>Different websites, different features, one goal: to enhance an agents online presence. Heres a recap of what makes this months selection of websites special:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Melanie Miller</strong>  Animated typography on the banner video hearkens to this top agents hands-on service.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Katie Reid</strong>  The interactive map lets browsers explore the various communities that Atlanta has to offer.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Lake Anna Home</strong>  Want to see how staging can transform a space? Let the before and after feature on this website show you.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Zac Mostame</strong>  Video walkthroughs of high-end homes exemplify this ace agents impressive property portfolio.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Jamie McMartin</strong>  Unique animation is applied to make the featured properties section a delight to explore.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Neil Spencer</strong>  This agents stylized signature is overlaid on listings as you hover and interact with it.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Red Frog Beach</strong>  Get in touch with agents ASAP thanks to the convenient WhatsApp chatbot.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>IMS Realty</strong>  The interactive map lets you take your pick among Las Vegas many excellent communities.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>HOME Luxury Real Estate</strong>  A section showcasing outstanding sales records highlights this teams many achievements despite being an upstart.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Katerina Sayles</strong>  This agents website boasts a section geared towards eco-conscious buyers.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Rethink your websites design</h3>\n<p>A great website is your gateway to a stronger brand and better lead generation. And we hope the sites listed above will inspire you to make the leap and get yours revamped, too.</p>\n<p>Do you want a website thats worthy of being included in our monthly list? Then get in touch with Agent Image today for a FREE design consultation. Just call <strong>1.877.317.4111 or send a message <a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/contact-agent-image/\">here</a></strong> to get started!</p>\n</div>\n<style>\n.custom-entry h2 {\n	line-height: 30px;\n	margi