s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:4;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:16:\"Agent Image News\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:5;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:23:\"Online Marketing Trends\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"https://www.agentimage.com/?p=25013\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:804:\"<p><img class=\"rss-ai-feed\" src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/banner-300x99.jpg\">Agent Image, the industry leader in real estate website design and digital marketing, adds another feather to its cap with the companys inclusion in the HousingWire Tech100 Real Estate list. With this accolade, the real estate design firm and marketing agency not only stands alongside the industrys most future-forward players, but also proves that its [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/blog/agent-image-honored-in-housing-wire-tech100-real-estate-list/\">Agent Image Honored in Housing Wire Tech100 Real Estate List</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.agentimage.com\">Best Real Estate Websites for Agents and Brokers</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:10:\"AgentImage\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4409:\"<img class=\"rss-ai-feed\" src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/banner-300x99.jpg\"><p><a href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/\">Agent Image</a>, the industry leader in real estate website design and digital marketing, adds another feather to its cap with the companys inclusion in the HousingWire Tech100 Real Estate list. With this accolade, the real estate design firm and marketing agency not only stands alongside the industrys most future-forward players, but also proves that its services have helped clients thrive in todays digital-first landscape.</p>\n<p>The HousingWire Tech100 Real Estate Awards recognizes the 100 technology companies that are changing the home sales process through innovation. In including Agent Image in this years honorees, HousingWire cited the companys ability to create best-in-class websites at scale. To date, the agency has launched over 25,000 websites for top-producing agents in all 50 U.S. states and across 38 different countries worldwide. These include sites for elite realtors like The Altman Brothers, The Oppenheim Group, Tracy Tutor, and Dolly Lenz, among others.</p>\n<p>For over two decades, Agent Image has leveraged technology to help agents and brokerages get ahead in an increasingly online-first world. Were thrilled to help our clients fast-track their digital transformation and this award from HousingWire reminds us why we do what we do, says Jon Krabbe, Co-Founder and Managing Partner at Agent Image.</p>\n<p>This latest accolade comes on the heels of Agent Images triumphs at the 2021 RealTrends Website Rankings, which saw the digital marketing firm collect 24 awards across 6 categories. Among its most notable wins was 3rd Best Overall Website for The Jills Zeder Group, the #1 real estate team in the nation.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/c1.jpg\" alt=\"Ginette Wright - VP for Marketing, Agent Image\" class=\"img-responsive\" /></p>\n<p>As part of its mission to further innovate real estate marketing, Agent Image has expanded its services beyond web design and digital campaigns. Just last year, the company launched its foray into the prop-tech space with <a href=\"https://www.access.com/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">ACCESS</a>, the first-ever Digital Listing Presentation and Digital Open House platform on the market. Developed in partnership with the leading real estate agents and teams in the country, ACCESS allows agents to easily create immersive and interactive branded presentations with the help of professionally designed templates and an intuitive user interface. The service is currently under beta testing, with free trials on offer to all interested agents and brokers.</p>\n<p>Were firm believers that technology amplifies success. To be part of a list that spotlights the most innovative companies working in real estate today is truly an honor, adds Vice President for Marketing Ginette Wright.</p>\n<p><script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n	{\n		\"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n		\"@type\": \"BlogPosting\",\n		\"mainEntityOfPage\": {\n			\"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n			\"@id\": \"https://www.agentimage.com/blog/agent-image-honored-in-housing-wire-tech100-real-estate-list/\"\n		},\n		\"headline\": \"Agent Image Honored in Housing Wire Tech100 Real Estate List\",\n		\"description\": \"The HousingWire Tech100 Real Estate Awards recognizes the 100 technology companies that are changing the home sales process through innovation.\",\n		\"image\":\n		[\n		{\n			\"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n			\"url\": \"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/banner.jpg\",\n			\"width\": 848,\n			\"height\": 284\n		}\n		],\n		\"author\": {\n			\"@type\": \"Organization\",\n			\"name\": \"Agent Image\"\n		},\n		\"publisher\": {\n			\"@type\": \"Organization\",\n			\"name\": \"Agent Image\",\n			\"logo\": {\n				\"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n				\"url\": \"https://www.agentimage.com/wp-content/themes/agentimage_v1/assets/images/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png\",\n				\"width\": 60,\n				\"height\": 60\n			}\n		},\n		\"datePublished\": \"2022-03-24\",\n		\"dateModified\": \"2022-03-24\"\n	}\n</script></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.agentimage.com/blog/agent-image-honored-in-housing-wire-tech100-real-estate-list/\">Agent Image Honored in Housing Wire Tech100 Real Estate List</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.agentimage.com\">Best Real Estate Websites for Agents and Brokers</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:37:\"https://www.agentimage.com/blog/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:15:\"updateFrequency\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:\"type\";i:128;s:7:\"headers\";O:42:\"Requests_Utility_CaseInsensitiveDictionary\":1:{s:7:\"\0*\0data\";a:10:{s:4:\"date\";s:29:\"Wed, 13 Jul 2022 03:42:02 GMT\";s:12:\"content-type\";s:8:\"text/xml\";s:13:\"last-modified\";s:29:\"Wed, 06 Jul 2022 14:02:32 GMT\";s:4:\"vary\";s:15:\"Accept-Encoding\";s:4:\"etag\";s:18:\"W/\"62c595f8-2d014\"\";s:16:\"content-encoding\";s:4:\"gzip\";s:15:\"cf-cache-status\";s:7:\"DYNAMIC\";s:9:\"expect-ct\";s:87:\"max-age=604800, report-uri=\"https://report-uri.cloudflare.com/cdn-cgi/beacon/expect-ct\"\";s:6:\"server\";s:10:\"cloudflare\";s:6:\"cf-ray\";s:20:\"729f019edb049fb5-SIN\";}}s:5:\"build\";s:14:\"20220215024450\";}', 'no');
